INSERT INTO registrants
            (email,
             first_name,
             last_name,
             gender,
             phone,
             country,
             school,
             level_of_study,
             minor,
             age,
             tshirt,
             driving,
             discord_tag,
             reimbursement,
             reimbursement_amount,
             reimbursement_desc,
             reimbursement_strict,
             accommodations,
             dietary_restrictions)
        VALUES
            (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
        RETURNING
            id
